node.text: you guys have been asking me how I curl my hair so I decided to do a quick tut 😌 now I’m no pro hairstylist but I do what I gotta do. tip for my @bellamihair curling iron….instead of clamping the whole part at once try twirling the section around the barrel and ONLY clamp the ends. This will ensure you get a wave instead of a spiral curl 💖 #bellamixamrezy link in bio to shop my tools 💋
